### Test API
GET http://localhost:3000/


### Get all reports
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reports

### Create report
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "animal": "Snake",
  "location": "IT Block",
  "date": "2026-06-04",
  "time": "14:30",
  "description": "Snake observed near the IT Block entrance.",
  "threatLevel": "🟡 Priority — Requires response"
}

### Update report
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/reports/<REPORT_ID>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Resolved"
}

### Admin Status Update Test (Should Succeed)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/reports/<REPORT_ID>/status
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Resolved"
}

### Student Status Update Test (Should Return 403)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/reports/<REPORT_ID>/status
Authorization: Bearer <STUDENT_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Resolved"
}

### Delete report
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/reports/<REPORT_ID>

